casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2005-2134. Preferred Capital, Inc. v. Power Eng. Group, Inc.

Summit App. No. 22475, 163 Ohio App.3d 522, 2005-Ohio-5113. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Summit County. Upon consideration of the application for dismissal of appellant Richard Oscar and Associates,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal is granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that the appeals of the other appellants remain pending.
